1990;;When You Remember Me;;American;;Harry Winer;;Kevin Spacey, Fred Savage;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/When_You_Remember_Me;;Mike Mills is a teen with muscular dystrophy, whose destitute single mother placed him in a state nursing home, where he contends with being a young person in the clinic and with an abusive head nurse, while Wade Blank started ADAPT, a grassroots national disability rights group in Denver in the 1980s.